description: World Fusion Cuisine is a truck roaming the streets of Lake Park and the surrounding areas, specializing in Latin cuisine fused with several others ranging from Asian and Italian to Middle Eastern, and many more. Check out the Ropa Vieja Tostones sliders, the Crispy Coconut Shrimp, the Middle Eastern Mezze, or just settle on a sampler platter of the ultimate favorites!
name: World Fusion Cuisine
